Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.13,0:22:44.13,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(55,43)}第76話  「荒川即興搞笑預選賽」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.30,0:22:47.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？怎麼不是漂流台
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.50,0:22:51.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來該輪到妮諾了  可她睡得死死的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.43,0:22:53.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法只好連床一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.74,0:22:55.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這要是掉下去了豈不是很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.76,0:22:58.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮諾小姐  我來了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.35,0:23:12.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮諾那傢伙  睡相還是這麼暴力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.86,0:23:17.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那是我傳授給沉睡妮諾的合氣道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.46,0:23:20.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？那可就是相當精彩的即興搞笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.14,0:23:22.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  是即興搞笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.49,0:23:23.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名曰  The
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.39,0:23:26.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡美人之怒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.39,0:23:26.48,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,床頭打架床尾和
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.49,0:23:28.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  還是你那個妙誒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.75,0:23:32.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修女  這個怎麼讀？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.52,0:23:33.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.11,0:23:33.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.71,0:23:34.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.30,0:23:34.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.87,0:23:35.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.26,0:23:36.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.14,0:23:36.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.28,0:23:38.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯黛拉  到時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.29,0:23:39.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  第10橋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.51,0:23:43.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是應該放棄交涉選擇武力啊
